y upvote the posts of Reddit<br />\n7. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。<br />\n8. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n9. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n10. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n11. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n12. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"592c97159e757b1d396c2a4cb67837758d95d120","tid":1532114,"uid":304726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"打起上黎美國民眾係最大受害者就真嘅，但至於邊個會輸得徹底啲就好難講。貿易戰唔係死加關稅就得嘅，美國有咁多靚牌打貿易戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3100066b3240d6c48a4599031d573a92381199","tid":1532114,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:34:12.000Z","msg":"有分析指<br />\n有消息指<br />\n有專家指"},{"pid":"6dd286984bcac23948caa833f41bc7619d553097","tid":1532114,"uid":39777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"有優勢就唔撚洗貶值啦屌<br />\n用下個腦都知啦"},{"pid":"8aaf16cd5830a0b644e6d9823dd4404ebb250625","tid":1532114,"uid":271617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDb6phTU8AE1NZZ?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEDb6phTU8AE1NZZ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=f623ff5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d92ed31611489b077fb0b344c80a0075462a6e4","tid":1532114,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實我係好支持 TVB 洗廢老腦的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0be9a1183d43c80fa3e0cc44f8c2d413758781bf","tid":1532114,"uid":30791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quot