3400d1ea9e4d9f2a295493f801639743a056","tid":1532114,"uid":287449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"d美國商人仲未意識到中共既威脅，其實睇5G就知咩事啦，唔講到底個技術係自己研發定偷番黎，已經有個新科技既市場比中國佔據左，仲以為自己可以靠賣野比中國賺錢？<br />\n依家囉住人地春袋唔揸，分分鐘以後反比人揸春袋，果陣唔好喊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借位宣傳<br />\n侵侵同d外國人都冇加你fb同ig，點知你想要咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再係facebook同ig自己圍爐打飛機啦，一齊黎開始國際戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個tweet幾秒鐘，一蚊都唔洗，又唔洗綁電話，安全又快捷，快d一齊轉用twitter啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">twitter文宣共識TG</span>： </span></strong><a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1altf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=0924cdb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n內有twitter詳細教學，開個account唔洗3分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文唔好驚比人笑？唔洗驚，國際文宣谷幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🔥<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>反送中 國際文宣谷link</strong></span></span>🔥<br />\n國際 Channel ：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo_int&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1altf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=10e4170e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"因為班商人仲賺緊中國人錢<br />\n覺得唔關自己事<br />\n當中國拎左佢地技術之後<br />\n就會開一樣既公司<br />\n仲會用更低價格同佢地打對台 <br />\n只睇短期利益 最後成間公司都失去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c6c70fc8e602c80c0ea002f2e2a90601f216e7","tid":1532114,"uid":53411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:31:37.000Z","msg":"Former Tesla employee admits uploading Autopilot source code to his iCloud<br />\n<br />\n前特斯拉員工承認他把自動駕駛的程式源碼上載到iCloud<br />\n<br />\nTesla believes he stole company trade secrets and took them to Chinese<br />\nstartup, Xiaopeng Motors<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉相信他偷了公司的商業機密並把它們帶到中國新創公司：小鵬汽車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGuangzhi Cao, a former engineer at Tesla, admitted in a court filing this<br />\nweek that he uploaded zip files containing Autopilot source code to his<br />\npersonal iCloud account in late 2018 while still working for the company.<br />\nTesla sued Cao earlier this year for allegedly stealing trade secrets related<br />\nto Autopilot and bringing them to Chinese EV startup Xiaopeng Motors, also<br />\nknown as Xmotors or XPeng, which is backed by tech giant Alibaba.<br />\n<br />\n（曹光植），前特斯拉員工承認他把Tesla自動駕駛的程式源碼上載到他的icloud。<br />\n特斯拉控訴曹把公司的自動駕駛的商業機密帶到中國的新創公司小鵬汽車，它是由<br />\n阿里巴巴支持的<br />\n<br />\nCao denied stealing sensitive information from the automaker in the same<br />\nfiling. His legal team argued he &ldquo;made extensive efforts to delete and/or<br />\nremove any such Tesla files prior to his separation from Tesla.&rdquo; Cao is now<br />\nthe &ldquo;head of perception&rdquo; at XPeng, where he is &ldquo;[d]eveloping and<br />\ndelivering autonomous driving technologies for production cars,&rdquo; according<br />\nto his LinkedIn profile.<br />\n<br />\n曹否認這個指控，他說他很努力的在離開特斯拉之前把所有跟特斯拉有關的檔案都刪了。<br />\n曹現在是小鵬汽車感知部門的頭頭，他負責發展汽車的自動駕駛技術<br />\n<br />\nAccording to a joint filing from the two parties that was also filed this<br />\nweek, Tesla has subpoenaed documents from Apple. While Apple is not involved<br />\nin this case, a former employee who worked on the tech company&rsquo;s secretive<br />\nautonomous car project was charged by the FBI with stealing trade secrets<br />\nlast July.<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉傳喚了蘋果的文件。雖然蘋果並沒有參與，但蘋果的前員工也涉嫌偷了特斯拉的<br />\n自動駕駛商業機密。<br />\n<br />\nThat employee allegedly Air Dropped sensitive data to his wife&rsquo;s laptop and<br />\nwas also caught on CCTV leaving Apple&rsquo;s campus with a box of equipment. He<br />\nhad left his job at Apple to take a position at XPeng before being arrested.<br />\nCao was also a senior image scientist for Apple for two years before he<br />\njoined Tesla, according to his LinkedIn profile.<br />\n<br />\n那個員工涉嫌利用Airdrop把敏感資料傳到他老婆的筆電並被抓到在蘋果的園區留下<br />\n一盒儀器。他後來離開了蘋果並在被捕前加入了小鵬汽車。曹在加入特斯拉前也<br />\n曾經是蘋果員工。<br />\n<br />\nThe suit comes at a time when the US is locked in a trade war with China and<br />\nhas accused the nation and some of its biggest companies of committing<br />\nso-called &ldquo;economic espionage.&rdquo; Tesla, Apple, XPeng, and a lawyer for Cao<br />\ndid not respond to requests for comment.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba3cf7d94aae199092fa628b9f0d31e373b1f4d","tid":1532114,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"大家要落力做文宣<br />\n風災捐少少錢畀美國<br />\n買人心"},{"pid":"fb15b9d5db26a4e14af6573ecf4dac5f3b5cb379","tid":1532114,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"CCTVB唔係出名燈嫁1咩"},{"pid":"4805fc6a9dd76526ed23309a6e7286923214078a","tid":1532114,"uid":111354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"早排睇到一條關於波蘭幾百年歷史既動畫片...唔知有高手可以整返條講香港歷史？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n得閒入黎睇睇"},{"pid":"5e9eae5626aeb79c03c8899eb1d8a1ee32d00122","tid":1532114,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac2fd559569694c1a286a79d41ccb29f62859338","tid":1532114,"uid":178875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/24/Tvb_hail_commie_winner.png/revision/latest?cb=20181215123622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvign